column1: NOTE: Data sent in report submissions will be “Support Data” under your agreement for Office 365 (or Skype), including any information that would otherwise be considered “Customer Data” or “Personal Data”.Please do not submit reports that may include data you do not wish to provide to Microsoft as “Support Data”.\n\nWe may not respond directly, but we do review and discuss every submission.
